Look at this.

5
00:00:02.902 --> 00:00:05.872
What that madman did.

6
00:00:06.072 --> 00:00:09.242
Carmine Falcone is
dead. and I'm here now.

7
00:00:13.580 --> 00:00:15.420
Gonna tear down the empire
from the inside-out.

8
00:00:19.819 --> 00:00:22.255
I've always known you
were capable of more.

9
00:00:30.964 --> 00:00:30.992
Ma

